    "visual_html": "<div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden font-sans max-w-full mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200 px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-3\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-purple-600\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n<span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 text-xs tracking-wide uppercase m-0\">Claude Code Prompt Template</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 md:p-8 bg-gray-50 flex justify-center\">\n<div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl bg-white border border-purple-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden flex flex-col transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:border-purple-300\">\n<!-- Header -->\n<div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-white px-4 py-1.5 border-b border-purple-100 flex items-center gap-3\">\n<div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner text-white\">\n<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 m-0\">Claude Code</div>\n<div class=\"ml-auto text-xs font-medium text-purple-600 bg-purple-100 px-2 py-1 rounded-full animate-pulse\">Analyzing prompt...</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Prompt Area -->\n<div class=\"p-4 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-700 bg-[#fbfbfb]\">\n<div>Build an <span class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold bg-blue-50 px-1 rounded\">Astro.js</span> website for the domain <span class=\"font-bold text-gray-900\">realonlineruler.com</span>.</div>\n<div class=\"mt-2\">It is an online ruler tool for phones and desktops.</div>\n<div class=\"mt-2\">Make it better than these competitors:</div>\n<ul class=\"list-disc ml-5 my-1 text-gray-500\">\n<li>[competitor1.com]</li>\n<li>[competitor2.com]</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"mt-2 text-purple-700 font-medium\">Analyze their weaknesses and suggest improvements.</div>\n<div class=\"mt-2\">Use the Web Design Guidelines and Tailwind skills.</div>\n<div class=\"mt-2 bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 p-2 rounded text-gray-800\">\n                    Include: ruler on all sides, calibration, dark mode, mobile responsive design, FAQ, and SEO content.\n                </div>\n</div>\n<!-- Footer / Action -->\n<div class=\"bg-white px-5 py-2 border-t border-gray-100 flex justify-between items-center\">\n<div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 flex items-center gap-1 m-0\">\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n                    Claude starts coding automatically\n                </div>\n<button class=\"bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-center gap-2 m-0 group relative overflow-hidden\">\n<span class=\"relative z-10\">Generate Code</span>\n<svg class=\"w-4 h-4 relative z-10 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7-7m7-7H3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg>\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "metadata_html": "<div class=\"mb-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">Why I saved this:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Keyword chip design</li><li>Clear conversational structure</li><li>Subtle border styling</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<h4 class=\"font-medium font-sans text-white text-sm mb-2\">What I can learn:</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 font-sans text-sm text-[var(--arsenal-text)] space-y-1\"><li>Structuring LLM outputs visually</li><li>Tag system UI patterns</li></ul>\n</div>\n<!-- RESTORED: SOURCE METADATA -->\n<div class=\"transparent p-4 rounded border border-white/20 text-sm mt-4 hidden\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-y-2 gap-x-4\">\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Creator:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Tejas Jaware</div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500\">Source:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><a class=\"underline font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:text-indigo-500\" href=\"paper_micro_tool.html\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">AI Micro-Tools Guide</a></div>\n<div class=\"font-mono text-gray-500 mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Rights:</div>\n<div class=\"col-span-2 text-gray-500 text-xs italic leading-tight mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-gray-200\">Belongs to original creator. Saved for inspiration.</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
